<div id="review_2808860391" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2808860391" />
    <a title="Kevin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/67532575-kevin"><img alt="Kevin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1635754429p2/67532575.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2808860391?book_show_action=true">Jun 02, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kevin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kevin" href="/user/show/67532575-kevin">Kevin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=science">science</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=religion">religion</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=psychology">psychology</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=short-reads">short-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/67532575-kevin?shelf=own">own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2808860391" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12829731962801537103">Whoever said that there are no absolutes in philosophy must have surely had the topic of free will in mind. I&apos;ve never heard more compelling arguments for such opposing points of view, each with its own existential hyperbole of quintessential conflubbery (yes, I just made up my own word, as a determinist I had no other choice).<br/><br/>If you&apos;re committed to the mental calisthenics necessary to tackle the tentacled titan that is Free Will, you owe it to yourself to seek out Daniel Dennett&apos;s &apos;Elbow Room&apos; </span>
  <span id="freeText12829731962801537103" style="display:none">Whoever said that there are no absolutes in philosophy must have surely had the topic of free will in mind. I've never heard more compelling arguments for such opposing points of view, each with its own existential hyperbole of quintessential conflubbery (yes, I just made up my own word, as a determinist I had no other choice).<br /><br />If you're committed to the mental calisthenics necessary to tackle the tentacled titan that is Free Will, you owe it to yourself to seek out Daniel Dennett's 'Elbow Room' for further reality altering points of view. Both are well written, though Harris is not as long-winded and Dennett is not as callous and self-absorbed. (wink, wink, nudge, nudge)</span>
  <a data-text-id="12829731962801537103" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


